de.jpdigital.owl.apigenerator.core

Class RepositoryGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.jpdigital.owl.apigenerator.core.RepositoryGenerator

  • public class RepositoryGenerator
extends Object
    Generates a repository class for each OWL class from the ontology. Each repository provides methods for
    • Retrieving all instances of a class
    • For each data property a method is generated thtat allows it to filter the instances for a specific value
    Author:
    Jens Pelzetter
